posting_body: ['RENTAL INFO', 'Rental Rates:', '$2175/month', 'Location:', '5200 Annapolis Ln N Plymouth, MN 55446', 'Unit for Rent:', '2-BR 2-BA |', 'Square Feet:', '1376 sq ft |', 'Lease Length:', 'Variable', 'show contact info', 'PROPERTY AMENITIES', '➢ Bike Storage', '➢ Car Wash Bay', '➢ Conference Room', '➢ Elevator', '➢ Free Weights', '➢ Gameroom', '➢ Picnic Area', '➢ Pool', '➢ Recycling', '➢ Resident Lounge', '➢ Barbecue/Grill Area', '➢ Basketball Half-Court', '➢ Cardio Machines', '➢ Complimentary DVD/Video Rental', '➢ Disposal Chutes', '➢ On-site Maintenance & Management', '➢ Planned Social Activities', '➢ Racquetball Court', '➢ Reserveable Clubhouse', '➢ Wake Up With Weidner Continental Breakfast', 'APARTMENT AMENITIES', '➢ Air Conditioning', '➢ Built-In Office/Desk', 'In Select Units', '➢ Dining Room', '➢ Full-Size Washer/Dryer in Every Home', '➢ Garbage Disposal', '➢ Linen Closet', '➢ Pantry', 'In Select Units', '➢ Patio/Balcony In Select Units', '➢ Vaulted Ceiling In Select Units', '➢ Walk-In Closets In Select Units', 'ADDITIONAL INFO', 'Description:', "The only thing that rivals Stoneleigh's exceptional property is our premium location that's just 15 miles northwest of Minneapolis.", "Here you'll have easy access to I-494, and a public bus stop is just steps outside our front door.", "The Reserve Park is a five-minute walk down the street: it's a great place to have a picnic, go for a walk, or let the kids run and play.", "Just down the road, you'll find Rockford Road Plaza where you can pick up necessities at Target, grab a quick burger at Five Guys, and discover the latest fashions at Kohl's.", 'Pet Policy:', 'Dogs and Cats Allowed:', 'Fees and deposits apply, please contact the community office for additional information.', '100 lb Weight Limit.', '2 Pet Limit.', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Stoneleigh at the Reserve:', 'show contact info', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', 'A4A7024A9456404']
